    "However, this is where we envision an important role for MDTs: to identify the requirements needed to actually deploy an Immune MDT (and thereby gain the benefits of digital twin technology), which can guide and focus research towards providing the necessary types of data- https://doi.org/10.1038/s41540-024-00345-5",
